  "title": "Accounts Associate (SNR / JNR)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Descriptions</strong></p>\n<p>The Associate will be entrusted with the following responsibilities:</p>\n<p>· Preparing full set accounts for a portfolio of clients</p>\n<p>· Preparing statutory financial statements and relevant supporting schedules</p>\n<p>· Supporting outsource processing functions such as generating sales invoices and credit notes and processing vendor invoices, expense claims and payments</p>\n<p>· Generating reports, including AR aging, P&amp;L, balance sheets</p>\n<p>· Preparing GST returns and basic tax computations</p>\n<p>· Liaising with clients and answering simple queries</p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>· Diploma in accountancy or business with a strong interest in accounting</p>\n<p>· Great attitude and takes initiative</p>\n<p>· 1 to 4 years experience</p>\n<p>· Fresh diploma graduates with an interest in developing a career in accounting are also welcome to apply</p>\n<p>· Excellent interpersonal skills</p>\n<p>· Competent in using MS Excel and Word</p>\n<p>· Knowledge of accounting software e.g Xero and Moneyworks would be an advantage</p>\n<p>· Understanding the various manpower regulations of Singapore would be an advantage</p>",
